    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Select one of the following arrays for your turret, which determines its damage type and range increment. You can spend 10 minutes modifying your turret using your custom rig to change its selected array.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Chaingun:</strong> 1d8 piercing damage, range increment 90 feet, analog trait, projectile weapon group</p></li><li><p><strong>Disintegrator:</strong> 1d8 acid damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, corrosive weapon group</p></li><li><p><strong>Laser Beam:</strong> 1d8 fire damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, laser weapon group</p></li><li><p><strong>Thunderclap:</strong> 1d8 sonic damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, sonic weapon group</p></li><li><p><strong>Volt Thrower:</strong> 1d8 electricity damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, shock weapon group</p></li><li><p><strong>Zero Emitter:</strong> 1d8 cold damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, cryo weapon group</p></li></ul>",
